cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper involves generating 3D shapes from natural language descriptions, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a method using Generative Adversarial Network (GAN), which is a popular deep learning technique and falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with generating high-quality shapes, which involves graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
